/onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1468-0335.2009.00803.x">working class and/or black</a> - groups which have been trending away from the party that is meant to represent them. Trump has been able to win voters over <em>simply by treating illegal immigration as a problem to be solved</em> .</p><p> In short, Trump&#39;s opponents get so mesmerised by his theatrics that they take their eye off his policies. His voters don&#39;t. </p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/five-myths-about-trump?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/five-myths-about-trump?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p><a href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/five-myths-about-trump">阅读更多</a></p>; 
